#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid "I'm not asking anymore.  Give me your stuff or else!"
msgstr "我不想再问了。把你的东西交出来，否则！"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid "Stick 'em up, <name_g>!  This is a hiest!"
msgstr "举起手来，<name_g>！这是抢劫！"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid ""
"How about you give me all your gear, and I let you walk away in one piece."
msgstr "不如把你所有的装备都给我，我就让你完整地离开。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid "You're gonna give me your gear, or get ripped to shreds."
msgstr "你要么把装备交给我，要么被撕成碎片。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid ""
"No, I think you're the one who's gonna back down.  Hand over your goods, "
"<name_g>."
msgstr "不，我觉得你才是该退让的那个。交出你的货物，<name_g>。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid "Now hand over your loot."
msgstr "现在交出你的战利品。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid "No, you'll be the one giving me your loot, if you want to live."
msgstr "不，如果你想活命，你才该把战利品交给我。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid "OK, OK.  I'm cooperating."
msgstr "好吧，好吧。我配合。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid "Lay your weapon on the ground, real slow like."
msgstr "把你的武器慢慢放到地上，动作要非常慢。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid "Let's see what you've got."
msgstr "让我看看你有什么。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid "You don't have anything else worth taking.  Get lost."
msgstr "你没什么其他值得拿的东西了。滚吧。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid ""
"[PSYCHO] Did you really think I'd let you live?  Nah, I'm going to kill you "
"anyway."
msgstr "[精神变态] 你真以为我会让你活吗？不，我无论如何都要杀了你。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid "[CANNIBAL] You still have to hand over all that tasty human meat."
msgstr "[食人族] 你还得交出所有那些美味的人肉。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid "[PREDATOR] Thank you for your cooperation.  Now you must die."
msgstr "[捕食者] 感谢你的配合。现在你必须死。"

#: .\TALK_MUG_NPC.json
msgid ""
"Regrettable, but I'm sure you understand that this is just how the world "
"works now.  No hard feelings?"
msgstr "很遗憾，但我相信你明白这就是现在世界的运作方式。没有恶意吧？"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Mugged By Player"
msgstr "被玩家抢劫"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Mugged By Player'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"AI tag for when NPCs have been recently mugged by the player.  This is a bug"
" if you have it."
msgstr "当NPC最近被玩家抢劫时使用的AI标签。如果你有这个标签，那是个bug。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Mug NPCs"
msgstr "抢劫NPC"

#. ~ Description for Mug NPCs
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Gives a few dialog options for robbing NPCs of their items without killing "
"them first.  Some available lines based on character traits. e.g. "
"psychopath, pacifist, etc.  Currently only works on dynamic and shelter "
"NPCs, not faction NPCs."
msgstr ""
"提供几个对话选项，用于在不先杀死NPC的情况下抢劫他们的物品。部分台词基于角色特质，例如精神变态者、和平主义者等。目前仅对动态NPC和避难所NPC有效，对阵营NPC无效。"
